Subject: [PATCH 1073/1179] HDFS-1001. DataXceiver and BlockReader disagree on when to send/recv CHECKSUM_OK

Reason: This patch is necessary for backport of HDFS-941 (socket reuse).
Author: bc Wong
Ref: CDH-3777
